# Grid reference cube — SANDS OF APOCALYPSE
# Exactly ONE grid tile: 2 x 2 world units on the floor, 2 units tall.
# The whole map's movement grid is 2-unit tiles, so design to this scale:
# import this cube, and every object should sit within a 2x2 footprint.
# Tile centres are 2 units apart; keep things centred on that spacing.
o GridReferenceCube
v -1.0 0.0 -1.0
v  1.0 0.0 -1.0
v  1.0 0.0  1.0
v -1.0 0.0  1.0
v -1.0 2.0 -1.0
v  1.0 2.0 -1.0
v  1.0 2.0  1.0
v -1.0 2.0  1.0
f 1 2 3 4
f 5 8 7 6
f 1 5 6 2
f 2 6 7 3
f 3 7 8 4
f 4 8 5 1
